column3: Most terms on this list came from most common Urban Dictionary terms
This list should not be viewed as "banned words on youtube"
You might have monetized videos that include these words
This list should be used as a reference, when trying to figure out why a video is yellow
These words were each tested in titles, one by one, and caused a video to go yellow
Some of these words can still be safe when used in certain context
The Demonitization bot is most strict with titles and descriptions
Having these words in the video dialogue is generally much less impactful
